# NAME: AI_Overseas
# AUTHOR: Kevin (kevshen13)
# REPO: https://github.com/kevshen13/surge-rules
# DESCRIPTION: Overseas AI services and global-route rule list for Surge
# UPDATED: 2026-04-15
# MAINTENANCE: Maintain this list by routing path, not by company nationality.
# RULE: Include domains/endpoints that should go overseas in actual use.
# RULE: If one vendor has both domestic and overseas versions, split by the actual route target.
# RULE: Keep broad keyword/domain rules conservative to avoid routing unrelated traffic.

